Package seng202.team4.model

Class Route

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team4.model.DataType
      • seng202.team4.model.Route
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validate
    public class Route
extends DataType
    Route model class with attributes representing the aspects of routes. These attributes were chosen from the open flights sample data. Objects of this class are created to display in the table on the route tab.
